import React from 'react';
import './App.css';
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import Books from './components/Books'
import ReadBooks from './components/ReadBooks'
import UnreadBooks from './components/UnreadBooks'
import AddBook from './components/AddBook'
import {Container, Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route} from 'react-router-dom' 


function App(){
  return (
    <Router>
      <Navbar/>
        <Container>
          <Row>
            <Col lg={12}>
              <Switch>
                  <Route path="/show-all" exact component={Books}/>
                  <Route path="/show-all-read-books" exact component={ReadBooks}/>
                  <Route path="/show-all-unread-books" exact component={UnreadBooks}/>
                  <Route path="/add-book" exact component={AddBook}/>
              </Switch>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Container>
    </Router>
  )
}
export default App;
